    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@Haroenv As expressed in https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/pull/4153#pullrequestreview-295442598, I wouldn't be comfortable introducing a new usage of the package for exposing a first codemod that does not fully address the problem. Right now, it makes the code work with v4 but leaves it in an \"unstable\" state where you still call multiple times `addWidgets()`. In my mind, we should solve the problem fully and not provide  a non-complete solution.",
